author: Xbox
description:
Join Hangar 13 live from PAX East for a developer panel hosted by Greg Miller of Kinda Funny Games, revealing new details and an exclusive behind-the-scenes look at Mafia: The Old Country.

► Timing: May 8, 2025 | 2PM ET / 7PM BST
► Wishlist Mafia: The Old Country now: https://mafiagame.com/

Uncover the origins of organized crime in Mafia: The Old Country, a gritty mob story set in the brutal underworld of 1900s Sicily.

Fight to survive as Enzo Favara in this immersive third-person action-adventure.
title: Mafia: The Old Country Developer Presentation - "Family Takes Sacrifice" | PAX East

description:
Jason and Lucia have always known the deck is stacked against them. But when an easy score goes wrong, they find themselves on the darkest side of the sunniest place in America, in the middle of a criminal conspiracy stretching across the state of Leonida — forced to rely on each other more than ever if they want to make it out alive. 

Explore Vice City and beyond at https://www.rockstargames.com/VI
